Planning a cozy Weekend in a offbeat location in North Bengal this Summers to experience the serene mountains and spend some relaxing time? 

Well, I have covered you up with the @bubblebliss91726, which is a very luxurious homestay situated in the Heart of Nature.

⭐️ This property has proper Geodestic Dome Setup, that too in North Bengal. Its a surreal experience staying there and enjoy a cozy time in the lap of mountains.

⭐️This luxurious Property has both luxury and semi luxury domes for all types of tourists.

⭐️Best part of the Resort is definitely the location- situated right beside the Gumbadara View Point

⭐️ They offer packages starting as low as Rs 1800 for Semi Luxury Dome and Rs 2200 for Luxury Dome per person per day which includes Lunch, Dinner, Evening Snacks and Breakfast! An amazing experience at a very reasonable price.

⭐️It has outdoor fireplace for delicious barbecues, free WiFi, and needless to say, breathtaking mountain view.

⭐️The foods served over here is fully homely, you will surely feel like you are having your Sunday’s lunch over here, with all delicacies made just like home.

The staffs were very punctual and helpful and made sure we spent our quality time there hassle free. The cleanliness of the property has to be the X-Factor undoubtedly. 

Rating: 4.8/5 ⭐️

Definitely a recommendation from my side. Suitable for Family, Friends and Couples.

⭐️Bubble Bliss
📌Tinchuley Lopchu Rd, beside New Jio Tower, Gumbadara, Peshok Tea Garden, West Bengal 734222
📞 9179172678, 8608029307
